comments: This is my specific field of interest, I think she did a great job at teaching the course. She\'s not boring, and is well spoken. Good job!

Graduate student who definitely knows her psychology. She pretty much goes directly off her slides, but you will need to read the book for reinforcement if you want an A. 5 quizzes and extra credit research. Highly recommend.

Rebecca is a graduate instructor that knows her psych material. It blows my mind that people would rate her lower because she didn\'t provide slides at the beginning of the year. We attend a university people...step up your game! Class expectations are extremely clear. Five tests and some research extra credit. Quite helpful. Definitely recommended.
She is young, energetic and definitely knows her stuff and she now provides the slides...highly recommend her!

She uses power point slides and explains the material while students are copying her slides...so if you try to listen to what she says then you miss the notes and they are not provided to the students on Blackboard or anything...her system DOES NOT work!
